These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, trance, soul
1. the fan of trance is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the fan of soul and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | milk | cola |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | punk    | soul   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, board-games, dancing
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, musician, mechanic
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the mechanic is between the librarian and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | baking    | dancing        | board-games |
| Job     | musician | mechanic | librarian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: fish, rat, mouse
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the owner of the rat and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk     | lemonade |
| Pet        | rat  | mouse | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, techno, blues
3 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, lizard
1. the fan of disco is the owner of the mouse##1
2. the fan of blues is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | blues     | disco |
| Pet           | turtle | lizard | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, hiking
3 different pets are kept: dog, snake, rat
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | hiking     | card-games |
| Pet     | rat    | dog | snake    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, spanish, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, climbing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is tennis is between the mexican and the british##2
2. the british is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | british  | spanish   | mexican        |
| Sport         | climbing | tennis | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pepper, asparagus
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, colombian, thai
1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the malaysian is between the person eating asparagus and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | pepper  | avocado  | asparagus |
| Nationality   | colombian | malaysian | thai     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, epic, disaster
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, russian, american
1. the person watching epic movies is the american##1
2. the russian is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | musical  | epic  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | russian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, skiing
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, scooter
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | skiing | cycling | parkour  |
| Transport   | scooter    | roller        | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
