.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, cauliflower, strawberry
1. the person eating strawberry is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda      | hot-chocolate      |
| Food       | cauliflower  | strawberry | kiwi |

