.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, techno
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, cricket, climbing
1. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is cricket##2
3. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | country | house   | techno   |
| Sport         | cricket | climbing | golf |

