.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, indian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, golf
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the brazilian and the indian##2
2. the brazilian is on the far left##1
3. the brazilian is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian   | indian   |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | handball |

