1. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching adventure movies##2
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure       | animation | action |
| Sport         | volleyball | biathlon | water-polo      |

