.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, r&b, salsa
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of r&b##2
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk   | cola |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | rock | r&b   |

 